sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_052_CSMS (Table 174, page 148/176)
    Note over CP,CS: Cancel Reservation - Rejected
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.17.3 - Cancel Reservation
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Reservation feature profile

    Note over CP: [Manual Action: Reserve a connector on the Charge Point]

    CS->>CP: 1. ReserveNow.req
    Note left of CS: connectorId: <Configured ConnectorId><br/>idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag><br/>reservationId: <unique id><br/>expiryDate: <future timestamp><br/>(params from TC_051, not listed in TC_052)

    CP-->>CS: 2. ReserveNow.conf (status: Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 3. StatusNotification.req (status: Reserved)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Reserved
    CS-->>CP: 4. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP: [Manual Action: Cancel the reservation on the Charge Point]

    CS->>CP: 5. CancelReservation.req
    Note left of CS: reservationId: <id>

    CP-->>CS: 6. CancelReservation.conf (status: Rejected)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Rejected

    Note over CP,CS: Central System processes the rejection
